{
  "stem": "162.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he said, they're giving you one more chance.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We're going back tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And for your incentive, if you do this scene, I have a big surprise for you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Anyway, we went back the next day, and I finally ended up doing the scene.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I remember-- I mean, in those days-- this is 1939-- there was the most beautiful toy stove, a metal toy stove filled with dishes and flatware and all kinds of pots and pans.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I mean, it was unheard of in those days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And that was my gift.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I did the film.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then shortly thereafter-- I remember the day so vividly-- we were told that Hitler was advancing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And everybody-- I remember my mother taping up all the windows with thick tapes because if the bombs exploded that the glass wouldn't crash on you.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I was in my same bedroom where I always used to look myself in the mirror and play my different parts, and I opened up the window, and I looked outside the window, and there suddenly was this tremendous explosion.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "A bomb had dropped in the courtyard between the two buildings, the one I told you about that I saw on the other side.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "A bomb had dropped and exploded.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Anyway, we rushed to the basement, to the shelter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But unfortunately, the shelter was on the other side, in the other building.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So while the bombs were falling all around us, we ran into that shelter across the lawn.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were people that were injured and people bleeding.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, my mother and I ended up in the shelter, what I think must have been days and weeks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think it was a month or so.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know how long the war was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
